<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#F7F5F0; font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;">

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#F7F5F0; padding:40px 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="520" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#fff; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #DDD9D2; overflow:hidden; max-width:520px;">

          <%# Cabeçalho %>
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#0F3826; padding:24px 32px;">
              <div style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:800; color:#fff; letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Practice-BR</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.7rem; color:#6EBD96; margin-top:3px;">
                <% if @lang == "fr" %>Plateforme de Portugais pour Étrangers
                <% elsif @lang == "en" %>Portuguese Learning Platform
                <% else %>Plataforma de Português para Estrangeiros
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Corpo %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:28px 32px 24px;">
              <div style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:12px;">🌿</div>

              <h1 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; color:#1C1917; margin:0 0 10px; line-height:1.3;">
                <% if @lang == "fr" %>Bonjour, <%= @student.name %> !
                <% elsif @lang == "en" %>Hey, <%= @student.name %>!
                <% else %>Oi, <%= @student.name %>!
                <% end %>
              </h1>

              <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#5C5853; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px;">
                <% if @lang == "fr" %>
                  Voici vos exercices disponibles cette semaine. À votre rythme, sans pression.
                <% elsif @lang == "en" %>
                  Here are your available exercises for this week. No rush — practice at your own pace.
                <% else %>
                  Aqui estão seus exercícios disponíveis no momento. Sem pressa — pratique no seu ritmo.
                <% end %>
              </p>

              <%# Lista de atividades — títulos sempre em português %>
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom:22px;">
                <% @activities.each do |activity| %>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:11px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #F0EDE8;">
                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                        <tr>
                          <td width="42" valign="top" style="padding-top:2px;">
                            <span style="display:inline-block; font-size:0.63rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:0.05em; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:20px; background:#DCFCE7; color:#15803D; white-space:nowrap;">
                              <%= activity.level %>
                            </span>
                          </td>
                          <td style="padding-left:10px;">
                            <div style="font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; color:#1C1917;">
                              <%= activity.title %>
                            </div>
                            <div style="font-size:0.73rem; color:#1A6B4A; font-style:italic; margin-top:2px;">
                              <%= activity.estimated_duration %>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %>
              </table>

              <%# Botão CTA bilíngue %>
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <a href="<%= @url %>" style="display:block; background:#1A6B4A; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; font-weight:700; border-radius:10px; text-align:center; padding:13px 22px;">
                      <span style="display:block; font-size:0.95rem;">Ver exercícios →</span>
                      <% if @lang == "fr" %>
                        <span style="display:block; font-size:0.72rem; opacity:0.75; font-weight:400; margin-top:2px;">Voir mes exercices</span>
                      <% elsif @lang == "en" %>
                        <span style="display:block; font-size:0.72rem; opacity:0.75; font-weight:400; margin-top:2px;">See my exercises</span>
                      <% end %>
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <%# Rodapé com opt-out %>
          <tr>
            <td style="border-top:1px solid #F0EDE8; padding:14px 32px 20px;">
              <p style="font-size:0.7rem; color:#B5B0AA; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">
                <% if @lang == "fr" %>
                  Vous avez activé le rappel hebdomadaire de Practice-BR.<br>
                  <a href="<%= student_dashboard_url %>" style="color:#9C9690;">Désactiver les rappels</a>
                <% elsif @lang == "en" %>
                  You enabled the weekly reminder for Practice-BR.<br>
                  <a href="<%= student_dashboard_url %>" style="color:#9C9690;">Turn off reminders</a>
                <% else %>
                  Você ativou o lembrete semanal da Practice-BR.<br>
                  <a href="<%= student_dashboard_url %>" style="color:#9C9690;">Desativar lembretes</a>
                <% end %>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
